                            br
                            | This is my first blog record and it will be a disclaimer until I find a better idea to introduce myself.
                            br
                            | You might ask (I hope you would) what is my reason? What is my purpose?
                            br
                            | I have a dream to become a coder, I've been learning the JS for some time, and one day I realised that I need something practical for deeper understanding what I'm learning. How this will help me to become a real coder.
            hr.my-1
            if formAvailable
                include body/newPostForm.pug
            .blog
                //- .mx-3
                    p.p-0.m-0.small='Sort by: '
                        a(href="#")= 'newest'
                        |  |
                        |
                        a(href="#")= 'oldest'
                        |  Show
                        |
                        a(href="#")= '20'
                        |  |
                        |
                        a(href="#")= '50'
                        |  |
                        |
                        a(href="#")= '100'
                each blogRecord in blog.blogRecords
                    include body/blogRecord.pug


        hr.my-2
        footer
